# Bangladesh Stock Market API - Test Endpoints
# Use this file with REST Client extension in VS Code or similar HTTP client

### Variables
@baseUrl = http://localhost:3000
@apiVersion = v1

### Health Check
GET {{baseUrl}}/health

### API Documentation (Root endpoint)
GET {{baseUrl}}/

### Test Hello Endpoint
GET {{baseUrl}}/{{apiVersion}}/dse/hello

### API Status
GET {{baseUrl}}/{{apiVersion}}/dse/status

### Get Latest Stock Data
GET {{baseUrl}}/{{apiVersion}}/dse/latest

### Get DSEX Data (All)
GET {{baseUrl}}/{{apiVersion}}/dse/dsexdata

### Get DSEX Data for Specific Symbol
GET {{baseUrl}}/{{apiVersion}}/dse/dsexdata?symbol=BEXIMCO

### Get DSEX Data for Another Symbol
GET {{baseUrl}}/{{apiVersion}}/dse/dsexdata?symbol=GP

### Get Top 30 Stocks
GET {{baseUrl}}/{{apiVersion}}/dse/top30

### Get Historical Data (All Instruments) - Last 7 days
GET {{baseUrl}}/{{apiVersion}}/dse/historical?start=2024-01-01&end=2024-01-07

### Get Historical Data for Specific Code
GET {{baseUrl}}/{{apiVersion}}/dse/historical?start=2024-01-01&end=2024-01-07&code=BEXIMCO

### Get Historical Data - Different Date Range
GET {{baseUrl}}/{{apiVersion}}/dse/historical?start=2023-12-01&end=2023-12-31

### Test Invalid Endpoint (404)
GET {{baseUrl}}/invalid-endpoint

### Test Historical Data with Missing Parameters (400)
GET {{baseUrl}}/{{apiVersion}}/dse/historical?start=2024-01-01

### Test Historical Data with Invalid Date Format (400)
GET {{baseUrl}}/{{apiVersion}}/dse/historical?start=invalid-date&end=2024-01-07

### Test Historical Data with Start Date After End Date (400)
GET {{baseUrl}}/{{apiVersion}}/dse/historical?start=2024-01-07&end=2024-01-01